This project is a Rust port of "simple-proxy.py" by spideynolove, originally
published as a public gist:

    https://gist.github.com/spideynolove/13785891385ed6916619ebb991b490b9

The original is a FastAPI/httpx reverse proxy for routing Claude Code requests
to multiple LLM providers. This project reimplements that functionality in Rust
(axum + reqwest + serde + tracing) with additional changes. Credit for the
original design and concept goes to the original author.
